#Text=Olympic highlights : August 9 , 2008
#Text=Saturday , August 9 , 2008
#Text=August 9 , 2008 is the first major day of the 2008 Olympic games , the below article lists some of the highlights .
#Text=Events
#Text=Men 's 10m air pistol
#Text=The Chinese Pang Wei took the gold medal in the final of Men 's 10 metre air pistol .
#Text=He achieved a total score of 688.2 in the final , 1.2 below the Olympic record of 690.0 that was set in the 2004 games .
#Text=The Silver medal went to the South Korean Jin Jong Oh and the North Korean Kim Jong Su won the bronze medal .
#Text=No new records were set in this event .
#Text=Women 's 10m Air Rifle
#Text=By winning four hundred points , the Czech Katerina Emmons equaled the previous world record and set a new Olympic record in the Women 's 10m Air Rifle .
#Text=Four hundred points is the maximum possible score in the event .
#Text=The Russian Lioubov Galkina won the silver medal with 399 points and a score of 103.1 in the final shots .
#Text=Snježana Pejčić from Croatia won the bronze medal with the same number of points as Galkina but a lower score in the final shots .
#Text=Women 's 48kg Weightlifting
#Text=The Chinese Xiexia Chen set a new Olympic Record with her total score of 212 in the Women 's 48kg Weightlifting event .
#Text=She got 117 of the points from the Clean & Jerk rounds and 95 of the points in the snatch rounds .
#Text=In second place , the Turkish Sibel Ozkan got 199 points .
#Text=111 of these points were from Clean & Jerk and 88 of them were from the Snatch rounds .
#Text=Wei-Ling Chen , from Chinese Taipei finished in third place with a total of 196 points .
#Text=Men 's Road Race

#Text=It was a very close finish between 6 competitors , all crossing the line practically at the same time , with Samuel Sanchez ( Spain ) in the lead , closely followed by Davide Rebellin ( Italy ) and Fabian Cancellara ( Switzerland ) in 2nd and 3rd place respectively .
#Text=Paolo Bettini , the favourite for the gold medal , has drilled during the race , and has reached the 16th place on the final leaderboard .
#Text=Women 's archery
#Text=Sung-Hyun Park , Ok-Hee Yun and Hyun-Jung Joo ( South Korean ) set a new record in the Womens archery with a combined score of 2004 .
#Text=Men 's 400m Individual Medley
#Text=The American Michael Phelps set a new Olympic Record in Heat four of Men 's 400m Individual Medley with a time of 4:07.82 .
#Text=This time was approximated two and a half seconds ahead of the person who finished second in the heat , the Italian Luca Marin .
#Text=Men 's 100m Breaststroke
#Text=The Norwegian Alexander Dale Oen set a new Olympic Record in Heat seven of Men 's 100m Breaststroke with a time of 59.41 seconds .
#Text=This time was approximately 0.4 seconds ahead of the person who finished second in the heat , the Australian Brenton Rickard .
